{"tid":578254,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"不要說「韓妝、韓式分界」，試著說「港妝、郭富城頭」","createTime":"2018-03-02T12:47:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-02T17:35:25.000Z","uid":106212,"like":76,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0f959dc28d5668258494e25356308b4a57c3f5df","tid":578254,"uid":106212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:47:52.000Z","msg":"所謂既韓式打扮，根本就抄 90年代香港明星既打扮<br />\n<br />\n粗眉、唇色深既「韓妝」？仲有「空氣瀏海」？你睇下後生時期既蔡少芬<br />\n<br />\n仲有咩「韓式分界」，廿年前叫做「郭富城頭」呀<br />\n<br />\n韓國人咁鍾意抄香港，仲要抄完都冇香港明星咁靚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n冇計啦，鬼叫韓國人先天不足 - <strong>眼細、面大、蒙古樣</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/02/202948_40bb1a9ed249617d17170bc580cfaae0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F02%2F202948_40bb1a9ed249617d17170bc580cfaae0.jpg&h=8ec2f708&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/01/213931_f9f6b400c375d93cec2e3d329ce308a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F01%2F213931_f9f6b400c375d93cec2e3d329ce308a1.jpg&h=d67b2e53&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"475b8a1729f001501251d301d7ff17a266209731","tid":578254,"uid":172915,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:48:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d67071a654a1a3357c608a2df9d66d39c0965ac","tid":578254,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:49:29.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"4fd540e5a679f82a1b5abf1cac2f3e8b024cfe98","tid":578254,"uid":89134,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:51:12.000Z","msg":"講真果句 香港好多明星都係天生麗質 靚仔<br />\n韓國人同支那北方人一樣都係好撚樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3278e8a61c07c6c9fe263f64b0c316b91fc4a96","tid":578254,"uid":106212,